  "texts": [
    "For example, the first cell represents the p-value corresponding to the factor \"GPT versions\", utilizing study design data evaluated by the ROUGE metric as input data for the ANOVA analysis.Evaluator Factor Study Design Sample Size Data Source Patient Intervention Comparison Outcomes ROUGE GPT <0.0001 0.0069 0.0107 <0.0001 <0.0001 0.0086 <0.0001 Prompt 0.0721 0.0005 0.0000 0.4689 0.9667 0.0022 0.9982 Interaction 0.0053 0.0134 0.9352 0.7269 0.9860 0.6483 0.9986 BERTScore GPT 0.0210 0.8896 <0.0001 <0.0001 <0.0001 0.0001 <0.0001 Prompt 0.3537 <0.0001 0.0000 0.9949 0.9470 0.0007 0.5658 Interaction 0.0554 <0.0001 0.9218 0.9934 0.9647 0.7438 0.2389 GPT GPT 0.0012 <0.0001 0.0011 <0.0001 <0.0001 0.0002 <0.0001 Prompt 0.0026 <0.0001 <0.0001 0.1556 0.8368 0.0434 0.1503 Interaction 0.0012 <0.0001 0.9431 0.8998 0.9806 0.6406 0.3165 In pair-wise comparison, GPT-4.0 tends to surpass GPT-3.5, particularly in complex tasks where direct answers are in the raw text.",
    "Table 4 demonstrated the significant edges of GPT-4.0 over GPT-3.5, characterized by both enhanced proportion of correctness and a reduced standard deviation, on Data Source (GPT-4.0: ‫‬ ௧ = 0.852; GPT-3.5, SD=0.32: ‫‬ ௧ =0.852, SD=0.38), Patient (GPT-4.0: ‫‬ ௧ = 0.924, SD=0.24; GPT-3.5: ‫‬ ௧ =0.844, SD=0.33), Intervention(GPT-4.0: ‫‬ ௧ = 0.688, SD=0.41; GPT-3.5: ‫‬ ௧ =0.568, SD=0.41), Comparison (GPT-4.0: ‫‬ ௧ = 0.804, SD=0.36; GPT-3.5: ‫‬ ௧ =0.764, SD=0.39), and Outcomes (GPT-4.0: ‫‬ ௧ = 0.864, SD=0.31; GPT-3.5: ‫‬ ௧ =0.706, SD=0.37).",
    "However, it is worth noting that GPT-4.0 may not necessarily outperform its predecessors.",
    "For example, GPT-4.0 does not reach the same level as GPT-3.5 on Sample Size (GPT-4.0: ‫‬ ௧ = 0.964, SD=0.16; GPT-3.5: ‫‬ ௧ =0.992, SD=0.08), even though the extraction is relatively simple and there tends to be a finite numeric answer in the abstract.Figure 3 visually compares the performance distribution of GPT-3.5 and GPT-4.0 on the seven items.",
    "Noticeably, it can be found that the performance improvement of GPT-4.0 is brought by shrinking tails near 0, which means the occurrence of all false values."
